{"tid":525753,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"柯達都出加密貨幣？","createTime":"2018-01-11T03:45:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T08:43:26.000Z","uid":28181,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fd813862655d66c7259612f45382bb084e2d9c3a","tid":525753,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T03:45:08.000Z","msg":"柯達都出加密貨幣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/REFRACTHK/posts/907306939447798\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FREFRACTHK%2Fposts%2F907306939447798&d=BAVET0n2BbFHwCCd4XesVCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=66f1b528\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/REFRACTHK/posts/907306939447798</a><br />\n//對很多人來說，柯達是一間老牌菲林公司，而且不知何時破了產(但現在已經債務重組完並重新起步)，但柯達最近搞作多多，昨日還宣佈新搞作：與WENN Digital合作，推出自家的區塊鏈和相片權利平台「Kodak One」，以及加密貨幣「Kodak Coin」。<br />\n<br />\n這個平台的原理是利用區塊鏈技術，追蹤平台上攝影師的相片是否被使用、在何處使用等資料，自動完成相片權利銷售，結算當然就是使用Kodak Coin。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/REFRACTHK/posts/907306939447798\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FREFRACTHK%2Fposts%2F907306939447798&d=BAVET0n2BbFHwCCd4XesVCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=66f1b528\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/REFRACTHK/posts/907306939447798</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/11/114507_92280d318e3a1a6f934376b27bf333e2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F11%2F114507_92280d318e3a1a6f934376b27bf333e2.png&h=8131c26b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb6dcced850d2893183f3b381d3b209d237add7a","tid":525753,"uid":71341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T14:57:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6fe3adf018278ec66913e751f372ce042421f7f","tid":525753,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb6dcced8